<div class="wrapper home-page">
  <div class="page-header first-section">
    <div class="banner">
        <%= image_tag "http://res.cloudinary.com/dbp2j1emu/image/upload/v1512406889/logo_epuuso.svg", class: "home-logo" %>
      <div class="nav-link">
        <a href="#how">How it works</a>
        <a href="#team">Team</a>
      </div>
      <h1>Find your dream Job</h1>
      <p>We create opportunities for you!</p>
      <%= link_to "Log in with LinkedIn", user_linkedin_omniauth_authorize_path, class: "btn btn-primary signup-button login-button" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class= "container text-center padded">
    <a name="how"></a>
    <h2 class= "secondtitle">How it works</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <p class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 seconddesc">To get started you will have to login with a LinkedIn account. If you don't have one you can make one for free here <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/">Linked In</a>. After you have logged in you can directly start searching for companies that fit your skillset via tools that they use in the company. Exampels: PHP, Ruby on Rails, Javascript. Now you browse the companies and find the ones that you like best. You will see contacts that you can add to your Leads dashboard. You can directly contact them by sending them an email or find them on LinkedIn. The Leads section allows you to keep track of everyone you want to contact and what progress you made.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-3">
        <i class="fa fa-user-plus fa-3x lp-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p>Sign Up,</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-3">
        <i class="fa fa-search fa-3x lp-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p>Search for a company via tools</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-3">
        <i class="fa fa-address-card fa-3x lp-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p>Add contacts based on your preferences</p>

      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-3">
        <i class="fa fa-handshake-o fa-3x lp-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p>Get hired</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="banner slogan layer">
    <h2>Create your opportunity on landing a good job</h2>
  </div>



  <div class= "container text-center padded">
    <a name="team"></a>


    <h2 class= "secondtitle">The Team</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <p class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 seconddesc">JobDetective has been created by Daniel Levelev and Alexander Pieczka. The website was made during a Le Wagon Bootcamp as Project.
      We wanted to improve the connection between developers and companies that are interested in hiring them.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
      <%= cl_image_tag("daniel_levelev-0f42d140ec3dfa5f1a4dcc187df433631b4312a89b923c9950853c83a8f5b30e_v5htfp.jpg", :gravity=>"faces", :width=>350, :crop=>"thumb", class: "avatar_super") %>
      <p>Daniel Levelev</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
      <%= cl_image_tag("Alexander_Pieczka_tpgk7u.jpg", :gravity=>"face", :height=>350, :width=>350, :crop=>"thumb", class: "avatar_super") %>
      <p>Alexander Pieczka</p>
    </div>
  </div>




  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="#">About</a>

      <a href="https://github.com/levelev/jobdetective"><i class="fa fa-github"></i></a>
      <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i></a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-copyright">
      2017 JobDetective  made this site with <i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
